Extract property one-column matrix by name

Extracts property one-column matrix by name

mdb_get_prop_matr1(mdb, propname)

Arguments

mdb

Molecular database
propname

Property name

Value

One-column matrix of property values

Examples

data("alkans74")
mdb_get_prop_matr1(alkans74.mdb, "bp")
